{
  "stem": "16106.5",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 465.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was on a truck, and we were fleeing the German-- the Russians, and I got sick, and I stayed with those people who, who were taking care of me while I was so ill.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now I was picked up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then this guy came again, what dates and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, listen, if I would have known you'll ask me a stupid question, I would have kept a diary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Ipso facto, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Catherine ?] would have said that, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they brought up the map and said, how did I come?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, I don't know very much of geographies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Surely, I said, I, I, I lost my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know where they are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm worried about them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then he said to me, never-- what did they arrest me for?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As a Russian spy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Never as a Jewess.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So if I said I'm not Russian, I didn't lie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I didn't know Russian then so much either, only a few words.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I know Russian better now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I did not lie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was very confident.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The only little-- that guy said, you know, I don't like your eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Something about your eyes I don't like.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I said, do you really?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I said, everybody admires my brown eyes and my blonde hair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Why don't you like it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Besides, I don't like your eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Your eyes are very dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Ah, he was-- he said, at that point, I said, I send you to room 79-- or 75, something in the 70s-- where you're going to meet Commandant so-and-so from the Gestapo, and he's going to take care of you.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
